      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study completed and GCI computed for pressure head and velocity magnitude. GCI for hemolysis index on fine mesh is 4.1%, exceeding the 2% threshold. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
