      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on geometry, operating conditions, and fluid properties representative of the COU VAD device and patient population.",
      "rationale": "Validation uses the FDA generic pump, which is geometrically dissimilar from the clinical VAD geometry. Operating conditions span 3 of 5 required flow-speed combinations. Relevance gap is significant. Achieved level 2 is below required level 4."
